$IJOY Roadmap

Phase 1 – Launch (Month 1)

• Deploy $IJOY on BSC / BNB Chain  
• Tradeable on flap.sh  
• Social media launch: Telegram & X (Twitter)  
• Initial 1% tax → encourage rapid adoption  

Phase 2 – Growth (Month 2–3)

• Increase tax to 3%  
• Fund charity wallet & marketing campaigns  
• Community rewards & reflections active  
• Launch NFT "LifeJoy Badges" for early supporters  

Phase 3 – Expansion (Month 4–6)

• Increase tax to 5% (optional) for sustainability  
• Charity transparency dashboard  
• Partnerships with NGOs & social initiatives  
• Meme competitions & viral campaigns  

Phase 4 – Long-Term Vision (Month 6+)

• LifeJoy becomes a recognized social-impact crypto movement  
• Integration into gaming, NFT & Web3 platforms  
• Continued rewards and reflections for holders  
